3. cs.AL (Computational Complexity) - The paper discusses the complexity of the vertex coloring problem in the Congested-Clique model, which is a topic of interest in computational complexity. 
4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with communication between nodes in a network, which falls under the purview of this sub-category.
